Cheating at Chess
A Game by JT Madden, Aadya Maurya, and Samantha Mroz


Controls:
* Click & Drag: Move Pieces
* Click: Navigate Menus and Buttons


Basic Walkthrough:
1. Tutorial
   1. Click and drag the X piece to the right-most white rook to destroy it
   2. Click and drag the remaining white rook up one square
2. Triangle
   1. Click and drag the X piece to the square directly below the black king to destroy it
   2. Click and drag the black rook down one square


Cheat Codes:
* Press R: Restart
* Press ESC: Exit full screen
